          <h1 class="ltr">Tesla Launches All-Vegan Car After PETA U.S. Appeal</h1>

          <div class="social-parent">
    <div class="social full notranslate">
      <a class="facebook"><i class="icon icon-facebook"></i><span>Share</span><span class="count"></span></a><span></span><a class="twitter"><i class="icon icon-twitter"></i><span>Tweet</span><span class="count"></span></a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="vote-box">
      <div>
